# Performance rules

- Target Lighthouse ≥ 90. Measure before/after for notable changes.
- Keep first-load JS lean: dynamically import heavy/client-only modules
  (three.js is already `next/dynamic`, `ssr: false`).
- Use `next/image` with correct sizes when images are added; fonts via
  `next/font` with `display: swap`.
- Avoid layout shift (reserve space); prioritize hero LCP, defer the 3D.
- Memoize expensive components; keep props stable to avoid re-renders.
- Use GPU-friendly transform/opacity animations; honor
  `prefers-reduced-motion`. Details: `.claude/CHECKLISTS/performance.md`.
